      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "JESSE RAIDER (1) turned in a plain run last time when sixth at this track over 300m behind It's Muffin Time (17.95) in a Novice race. Was in the money the start prior. Worth another chance. BUTCH FRANKY (2) doesn't win out of turn. Hit the board with a minor placing last time when second (17.50) at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Leading player again. TURNOVER (3) was resuming when finishing seventh at Northam in a Grade 5/6 (18.36). Will be much improved. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Key player if finds best. WEDGE RUN (8) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.",
